<h1>1. Tokenizer</h1>

<p>The <span class="emph">Tokenizer</span> program is used to generate tokens from a
<span class="emph">PeerId</span> to create receiving email addresses for Pond users.
You can either download a ready-to-use program version or compile your own.</p>

