<p>If the program provided here for your platform does not work on your computer,
you have to compile the application yourself.</p>

<h2>1.2. Compile the program yourself</h2>

<p>The program is (just like Pond or the gateway) written in a programming language called
<a href="https://golang.org" target="_blank">Go</a>. To compile this tools you need to have
a development environment for Go first. Go to the
<a href="https://http://golang.org/doc/install" target="_blank">project website</a>
to learn on how to do that.</p>

<p>Download the <a href="files/tokenize.go" target="_blank">source code</a>
for the tool and store it on your computer. To compile the program you issue the following command:</p>

<p class="code">$ go build -o tokenize tokenize.go</p>

